<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Commerce Career Path</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="stream-detail.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header class="stream-hero">
    <span>Business Stream</span>
    <h1>Commerce Career Path</h1>
    <p>Commerce is about money, business, accounting, markets, management, taxation, and entrepreneurship. It is ideal for students who enjoy numbers, planning, leadership, and decision-making.</p>
  </header>
  <main class="stream-shell">
    <section class="quick-grid">
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Main Subjects</strong>Accounts, Economics, Business Studies, Maths</div>
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Common Exams</strong>CUET, CA Foundation, CS Executive Entrance, college tests</div>
      <div class="quick-card"><strong>Best For</strong>Finance, business, analysis, management</div>
    </section>
    <h2 class="section-title">Popular Commerce Fields</h2>
    <section class="path-grid">
      <div class="path-card active"><h3>Accounting</h3><p>Work with financial records, auditing, taxation, and compliance.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Management</h3><p>Lead teams, plan business growth, and manage operations.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Finance</h3><p>Explore banking, investments, insurance, markets, and analysis.</p></div>
      <div class="path-card"><h3>Entrepreneurship</h3><p>Build startups, understand customers, and solve market problems.</p></div>
    </section>
    <section class="tabs">
      <button class="tab-btn active" data-target="courses">Courses</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="exams">Entrance Exams</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="careers">Careers</button>
      <button class="tab-btn" data-target="skills">Skills</button>
    </section>
    <section class="detail-panel">
      <div id="courses" class="tab-panel active"><h2>Courses You Can Choose</h2><ul><li>B.Com, B.Com Honours, BBA, Economics Honours.</li><li>CA, CS, CMA, Banking and Insurance courses.</li><li>MBA later for management and leadership roles.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="exams" class="tab-panel"><h2>Entrance Exams</h2><ul><li>CUET for many central universities.</li><li>CA Foundation for Chartered Accountancy.</li><li>College or university entrance tests for BBA and Economics.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="careers" class="tab-panel"><h2>Career Options</h2><ul><li>Chartered Accountant, Accountant, Banker, Financial Analyst.</li><li>Business Manager, Marketing Executive, HR Executive, Entrepreneur.</li><li>Tax Consultant, Auditor, Investment Advisor.</li></ul></div>
      <div id="skills" class="tab-panel"><h2>Skills To Build</h2><ul><li>Accounts, Excel, communication, and analytical thinking.</li><li>Market awareness, budgeting, presentation, and negotiation.</li><li>Ethics and accuracy while handling financial data.</li></ul></div>
    </section>
    <section class="planner"><h2>Student Checklist</h2><label><input type="checkbox"> Practice accounts problems regularly.</label><label><input type="checkbox"> Compare B.Com, BBA, CA, and Economics paths.</label><label><input type="checkbox"> Learn spreadsheet basics for finance work.</label></section>
    <div class="back-row"><a class="action-link" href="career.jsp">Back to Career Streams</a></div>
  </main>
  <script src="stream-detail.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
